parameters: Oho! Welcome! \!I don't usually see people around here...
You can call me what everyone else calls me - the Draining Witch.
Have you heard all that gossip about me?

\!
Well, don't be afraid. I don't go around stealing memories from travelers in the forest.
At least... not without their permission.
See, I *love* memories! I put them in Elixirs and observe them. \!But that's not all they do!
If one drinks an Elixir, they gain a wealth of knowledge and experience... just like that!
If you're curious... Then see for yourself! â™¥

\!
If you like, I can \C[23]drain your memories as well.
But I'm not asking so I can keep them!

\!
In fact, \C[23]I'll let you turn a teammate's memories into an Elixir for someone else to use.
Ah, you're back! Thirsty for more memories~?

\!
Who shall I be draining from today~?
Ah, so you've been changed in some "irreversible" way.
I can do something about it...\! but I'll have to drain your memories for it to work.
That said, who's the one in need of my assistance?
Ah, I *do* sense memories within, but...
